obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (39695)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title.`
  content `This Act may be called the Pondicherry (Extension of Laws) Act, 1968.`
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39695&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (39696)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definitions.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39696&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,—`
  line
  line `(a) “Act” means an Act or the Ordinance specified in the Schedule;`
  line
  line `(b) “Administrator” means the administrator of Pondicherry appointed by the President under article 239 of the Constitution;`
  line
  line `(c) “Pondicherry” means the Union territory of Pondicherry.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (39697)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Extension with amendments of certain laws to Pondicherry and their commencement therein.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39697&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Acts specified in Part I of the Schedule as they are generally in force in the territories`
  line `to which they extend and the Acts specified in Part II of the Schedule as they were in force on the 1st day`
  line `of August, 1966, in the State or Union territory mentioned there against shall extend to Pondicherry,`
  line `subject to the modifications, if any, specified in the Schedule.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section (1), or in the relevant provision, if any, of each`
  line `such Act for the commencement thereof, the provisions of each such Act shall come into force in`
  line `Pondicherry on such date as the Administrator may, by notification in the Official Gazette, appoint:`
  line
  line `Provided that different dates may be appointed for different provisions of any Act and any reference`
  line `in any such provision to the commencement of the Act shall be construed as a reference to the coming`
  line `into force of that provision.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (39698)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Repeal and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39698&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `(1) Any law in force in Pondicherry or any area thereof corresponding to any`
  line `Act referred to in sub-section (1) of section 3 or any part thereof (except in so far as such law continues to`
  line `be applicable to Renoncants) shall stand repealed as from the coming into force of such Act in`
  line Pondicherry.
  line
  line `(2) Nothing in sub-section (1) shall effect—`
  line
  line `(a) the previous operation of any law so repealed or anything duly done or suffered thereunder; or`
  line
  line `(b) any right, privilege, obligation or liability acquired, accrued or incurred under any law so`
  line `repealed; or`
  line
  line `(c) any penalty, forfeiture or punishment incurred in respect of any offence committed against`
  line `any law so repealed; or`
  line
  line `(d) any investigation, legal proceeding or remedy in respect of any such right, privilege,`
  line `obligation, liability, penalty, forfeiture or punishment as aforesaid,`
  line
  line `and any such investigation, legal proceeding or remedy may be instituted, continued or enforced and any`
  line `such penalty, forfeiture or punishment may be imposed as if this Act has not been passed:`
  line
  line `Provided that anything done or any action taken (including any appointment or delegation made,`
  line `notification, instruction or direction issued, form, bye-law or scheme framed, certificate obtained, permit`
  line `or licene granted, or registration effected) under any such law, shall be deemed to have been done or`
  line `taken under the corresponding provision of the Act extended to Pondicherry by this Act and shall`
  line `continue to be in force accordingly unless and until superseded by anything done or any action taken`
  line `under the said Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (39699)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Extension of rules, orders, etc., under certain laws.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39699&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `All rules, notifications, orders, regulations`
  line `and bye-laws made or issued by the Central Government under the provisions of any Act generally for the`
  line `territories to which such Act extends shall, as from the commencement of the provisions of such Act in`
  line `Pondicherry, extend to, and come into force in, Pondicherry.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (39700)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Rules of construction.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39700&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `(1) In any Act or in any of the rules, notifications, orders, regulations and`
  line `bye-laws made or issued thereunder and extended to Pondicherry by this Act,—`
  line
  line `(a) any reference to any provision of law not in force, or to any functionary not in existence, in`
  line `Pondicherry shall be construed as a reference to the corresponding law in force, or to the`
  line `corresponding functionary in existence, in that Union territory:`
  line
  line `Provided that—`
  line
  line `(i) if any question arises as to who such corresponding functionary is, or`
  line
  line `(ii) if there is no such corresponding functionary, the Administrator shall decide as to who`
  line `such functionary will be and his decision shall be final;`
  line
  line `(b) any reference to the State Government shall be construed as a reference to the Central`
  line `Government and also as including a reference to the Administrator.`
  line
  line `(2) For the purpose of facilitating the application in relation to Pondicherry of any Act or any rule,`
  line `notification, order, regulation or bye-law made or issued thereunder, any court or other authority may`
  line `construe it in such manner, not affecting the substance, as may be necessary or proper to adapt it to the`
  line `matter before the court or other authority.`
obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_7:
  sectionId (39701)
  sectionNo (7)
  orderNo 7
  title `Power to remove difficulties.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_7_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284&sectionId=39701&sectionno=7&orderno=7&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00018_196826_1517807320284
obj_root_law_sections_7_content:
  string
  line `If any difficulty arises in giving effect in Pondicherry to the`
  line `provisions of any Act extended by this Act to Pondicherry, the Central Government may, as occasion may`
  line `require, by order, make such provisions or give such directions not inconsistent with the provisions of`
  line `such Act as appear to it to be necessary for the purpose of removing the difficulty and any such order may`
  line `provide for the transfer of any matter pending before any court, tribunal or other authority immediately`
  line `before the commencement of such Act in Pondicherry to any corresponding court, tribunal or authority`
  line `for disposal:`
  line
  line `Provided that no such order shall be made under this section in respect of any Act after the expiration`
  line `of two years from the date on which such Act comes into force in Pondicherry and in respect of an Act,`
  line `the provisions of which are brought into force in Pondicherry on different dates, the period of two years`
  line `shall be reckoned with reference to the commencement of the relevant provision as specified in the`
  line `proviso to sub-section (2) of section 3.`
obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes:
  string
  line
